                        <lb/>Easby Church neare Rich: y<hi rend="superscript">e</hi> next morn
                        <lb/>ing; y<hi rend="superscript">e</hi> efects of w<hi rend="superscript">ch</hi> sicknesse lasted by
                        <lb/>an Ague, feauer, &amp; Iaundies 3 q<hi rend="superscript">rters</hi> of a
                        <lb/>yeare; at hipswell.
