                        <lb rend="indent"/> 1652 <!-- ideally centred-->
                        <lb/>I began my great sickeness after	
                        <lb/>I came from Burn Park the first time
                        <lb/>about the 6<hi rend="superscript">th</hi> of August 1652 and miscar-
